Available Tools: get_stock_level | check_availability | get_low_stock_items | get_stock_by_location
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "sku": "string", "location_id": "string", "threshold": number }
Response Schema: { "sku": "string", "product_name": "string", "quantity": number, "location": "string", "status": "in_stock|low_stock|out_of_stock" }
---
Question: What is the current quantity of the ergonomic office chair in the Houston fulfillment center?
Call: { "func_call": "get_stock_level", "sku": "CHR-ERG-01", "location_id": "HOU-FC-03", "threshold": 30 }
Response: { "sku": "CHR-ERG-01", "product_name": "Ergonomic Mesh Office Chair", "quantity": 125, "location": "HOU-FC-03", "status": "in_stock" }

